==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Circumspectness
<hw>Cir"cum*spect"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Vigilance in guarding
against evil from every quarter; caution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[Travel] forces <qex>circumspectness</qex> on those abroad, who at
home are nursed in security.</q> <rj><qau>Sir H. Wotton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>circumstance</ent>⟦br⟧
